      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ember_vein_1e_006",
      "speaker": "cael",
      "lines": [
        "Edren. Those murals. The figures weren't holding the",
        "Pendulum up. They were holding something back."
